                    <span>The book was great, and completely worth it.  My riding took a leap in no time.  I completely recomend this book, I loved reading it and I love riding.  Make sure if you get it to read it starting with chapter 1 and read everything, dont skip around.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Worth its weight in gold!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
